From b1ef799019802ddd3efdf069ac5c848c7c0576b6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 14:12:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove tray methods from IGuiAdapter, expose TryToExit as
 public

Tray management (ShowTray, HideTray, SetTrayText, SetTrayIcon) is now
the responsibility of the GUI framework (Avalonia) rather than the
abstract adapter interface.

TryToExit is made public so the GUI layer can call it directly from
tray menu handlers.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01JfhdSkGJLjsqv5VzRK8FA8
