 Bakabase.Infrastructures/Components/Gui/GuiAdapter.cs  | 9 ---------
 Bakabase.Infrastructures/Components/Gui/IGuiAdapter.cs | 5 -----
 3 files changed, 1 insertion(+), 16 deletions(-)

